# ğŸ›’ Smart Shopping Companion

> A personal tool to save money through intelligent price tracking and store comparison.

## ğŸ“– The Story

I created this app because flyer shopping was eating hours of my timeâ€”jumping between stores, manually converting units, forgetting what I paid last week. This app is my solution, built during my 90-day journey to AI-technical fluency.

## âœ¨ Vision

A mobile-first shopping app that:
- **Tracks price history** - Never forget what you usually pay
- **Converts units automatically** - Compare $/100g across all stores
- **Compares stores** - See which store saves you the most TODAY
- **Optimizes trips** - Is store-hopping worth the savings?
- **Learns over time** - Your personal price intelligence database

## ğŸ¯ Core Features (Phase 1 - MVP)

### Must-Have (Weeks 1-8)
- [ ] Create and manage multiple shopping lists
- [ ] Add items with price, unit, store, date
- [ ] Automatic unit price conversion ($/100g, $/lb, $/kg)
- [ ] Price history tracking per item
- [ ] Store comparison dashboard
- [ ] Cost estimation per list

### Nice-to-Have (Weeks 9-12)
- [ ] Trip optimizer (single vs. multi-store)
- [ ] Visual price history graphs
- [ ] Urgency tagging system
- [ ] Mobile-responsive design
- [ ] Cloud sync across devices

## ğŸš€ Phase 2 Vision (Days 91-180)
- OCR flyer scanning
- Recipe import
- AI-powered suggestions
- Family sharing
- Premium features

